org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.catalog.resource
Class AeResourceCache

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.catalog.resource.AeResourceCache
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeConfigChangeListener, IAeResourceCache
public class AeResourceCache
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAeResourceCache, IAeConfigChangeListener

In memory cache for resource objects with a max upper limit. Default value, if not in config, is 50.
